p.strong: Turn in dates for the April 9th – 17th period will be April 20th, 21st, and 22nd. Packets for all schools can be turned in at the Junior High main entrance (2110 Hwy 94 N, Camp Point). This can be done any time of day. There will be a bin for each building inside the first set of doors.
The next round of packets will be mailed out on 4/20.
